PN,30501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FAn Islamist group with possible links
OL,7,Fto the Iranian regime has claimed
OL,8,Fresponsibility for an arson attack on
OL,9,FJewish community ambulances in North
OL,10,FLondon, with police investigating the
OL,11,Fassertion.
OL,13,FFour ambulances from Hatzola, a Jewish-
OL,14,Fled service run by volunteers, were
OL,15,Fset on fire in Golders Green during
OL,16,Fthe early hours of Monday, in what the
OL,17,FMet Police are treating as an
OL,18,Fantisemitic hate crime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FA video allegedly posted on Telegram
OL,7,Fby Islamist group Harakat Ashab al-
OL,8,FYamin al-Islamia showed a map of the
OL,9,Flocation where the ambulances were
OL,10,Fkept and footage of them on fire.
OL,12,FHead of the Met Police Sir Mark Rowley
OL,13,Fsaid there had been "rapid growth" of
OL,14,FIranian state threats in the UK, but
OL,15,Fdeclared it too early to determine who
OL,16,Fwas behind the ambulances attack.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,F"The rapid growth in recent years of
OL,7,FIranian state threats is grave:
OL,8,Fhostile state surveillance activity,
OL,9,F20 disrupted plots, and recent
OL,10,Fattempted attacks on the Iranian
OL,11,Fdiaspora," Rowley said during the
OL,12,Fannual dinner of the Community
OL,13,FSecurity Trust (CST), a charity that
OL,14,Fmonitors antisemitism in the UK, on
OL,15,FMonday.
OL,17,F"None of this is isolated. It is part
OL,18,Fof a rapidly shifting threat landscape.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,F"It is too early for me to attribute
OL,7,Flast night's attack in Golders Green
OL,8,Fto the Iranian state ` that is rightly
OL,9,Ffor the counter-terrorism
OL,10,Finvestigation to determine ` but
OL,11,Fwhoever was responsible, the impact is
OL,12,Fserious.
OL,14,F"We believe three suspects were
OL,15,Finvolved and we are pursuing all lines
OL,16,Fof inquiry, including an online claim
OL,17,Fof responsibility by an Islamist group
OL,18,Fwho have claimed other attacks across
OL,19,FEurope and have potential Iranian
OL,20,Fstate links."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism police are leading
OL,7,Fthe investigation and they say more
OL,8,Fthan 200 extra officers will be
OL,9,Fdeployed to protect Jewish communities
OL,10,Fin the wake of the attack.
OL,12,FThey are also looking at the apparent
OL,13,Fclaims by Harakat Ashab al-Yamin al-
OL,14,FIslamia.
OL,16,FAssistant Commissioner Laurence Taylor
OL,17,Fsaid: "That is one of the lines of
OL,18,Finquiry that we are progressing.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,F"We know that online, they have laid
OL,7,Fclaim to a number of incidents across
OL,8,FEurope, and so it's obviously very
OL,9,Fimportant for us to understand what is
OL,10,Fbehind the attack in Golders Green,
OL,11,Fand what the motivation of those
OL,12,Findividuals was.
OL,14,F"But critically, we want to get them
OL,15,Finto custody as quickly as we can and
OL,16,Fbring them to justice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FPolice and the security services have
OL,7,Fincreasingly seen hostile states
OL,8,Fincluding Iran, China and Russia using
OL,9,Fproxies to carry out subversive
OL,10,Factivities on UK soil.
OL,12,FRowley continued: "Britain's Jewish
OL,13,Fcommunity has in recent years been
OL,14,Fincreasingly targeted by individuals,
OL,15,Fgroups and hostile states, intent on
OL,16,Fspreading fear, hate and harm.
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,F"This volatile mix is at the front of
OL,7,Fmy mind given events of today."
OL,9,FCCTV footage of the arson attack
OL,10,Fshowed three people in hoods pouring
OL,11,Faccelerant on the ambulances, setting
OL,12,Fthem on fire and running away during
OL,13,Fthe early hours of Monday.
OL,15,FIt is being treated as an antisemitic
OL,16,Fhate crime, but not a terrorist act,
OL,17,FScotland Yard has said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FRowley praised the "extraordinary
OL,7,Fspeed and professionalism" of local
OL,8,Fvolunteers, CST teams, synagogue
OL,9,Fsecurity and Hatzola staff, which he
OL,10,Fsaid "quite literally protected
OL,11,Flives", alongside the actions of Met
OL,12,Fofficers.
OL,14,FCCTV shows three people in hoods
OL,15,Fpouring accelerant on the vehicles.
OL,16,FCredit: Jewish Community Council
OL,18,F"Let us be clear about what was
OL,19,Ftargeted: a volunteer ambulance
OL,20,Fservice that serves everyone, of every
OL,21,Fbackground," he continued.
OL,26,@nD@TOUoD@ZO]rD@FOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,F"An attack on Hatzola is not only an
OL,7,Fattack on the Jewish community but an
OL,8,Fattack on all of us."
OL,10,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer condemned
OL,11,Fthe attack on the ambulances on Monday
OL,12,Fmorning, describing it as a "horrific
OL,13,Fantisemitic attack" and stating that
OL,14,Fhe had been in touch with community
OL,15,Fleaders.
OL,17,F"Antisemitism has no place in our
OL,18,Fsociety and it's really important that
OL,19,Fwe all stand together in a moment like
OL,20,Fthis," Starmer said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,7,Fconfirmed that the government will
OL,8,Ffund replacement ambulances for the
OL,9,Fcommunity, as well as supplying
OL,10,Fimmediate health support.
OL,12,FThe ambulances were set alight on
OL,13,FHighfield Road at about 1.45am on
OL,14,FMonday. Gas canisters kept in the
OL,15,Fvehicles exploded in the fire and the
OL,16,Fforce shattered nearby windows,
OL,17,Fincluding those of a synagogue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FNo injuries were reported, and six
OL,7,Ffire engines with around 40
OL,8,Ffirefighters attended the scene to
OL,9,Ffight the blaze.
OL,11,FOne man, who lives in Highfield Road,
OL,12,Fsaid: "My wife was afraid for her
OL,13,Flife. People were shouting to just
OL,14,Fgrab a bag and leave but did not tell
OL,15,Fus where to go. It was very scary and
OL,16,FI'm still shaking now."
OL,26,@tD@GOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774357890
OL,3,CPolice investigating possible Iran
OL,4,Clink to attack on Jewish ambulances
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Luke
OL,7,FWilliams, who leads policing for the
OL,8,Farea, said on Monday investigators are
OL,9,Faware of a group apparently claiming
OL,10,Fresponsibility for the attack online,
OL,11,Fbut confirmed this had not been
OL,12,Fverified.
OL,14,FJewish leaders met Starmer in Downing
OL,15,FStreet on Monday, and Michael Wegier,
OL,16,Fchief executive of the Board of
OL,17,FDeputies of British Jews, said Jews in
OL,18,Fthe UK feel less safe now than in the
OL,19,Fyears previous.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
